00:35:48.780 --> 00:35:54.580
as a resident in International
Writing Program and I want

00:35:54.580 --> 00:35:58.040
to say this, it's an honor
to be in front of you,

00:35:58.040 --> 00:35:59.430
my colleagues in the program.

00:35:59.430 --> 00:36:03.510
For the last time
at least for once.

00:36:03.510 --> 00:36:13.100
