00:49:21.790 --> 00:49:24.050
I think I can give a
really clear example,

00:49:24.050 --> 00:49:27.500
so my first visitor, as I
mentioned, was Carolyn Forshay.

00:49:27.500 --> 00:49:30.430
This was during the George
W. Bush administration time.

00:49:30.430 --> 00:49:34.410
And she had some differences
with official policy

00:49:34.410 --> 00:49:36.560
and so she gave a lot of
interviews and in some

00:49:36.560 --> 00:49:39.640
of them she spoke against
official U.S. policy

00:49:39.640 --> 00:49:41.640
and so I consulted
my boss, you know,

00:49:41.640 --> 00:49:45.190
as a new officer what is
a guideline and he said,

00:49:45.190 --> 00:49:47.220
