somebody was being paid

00:50:07.490 --> 00:50:09.680
by the government
on the program had

00:50:09.680 --> 00:50:11.400
to speak that government line.

00:50:11.400 --> 00:50:13.370
And for them, that
idea of freedom

00:50:13.370 --> 00:50:16.560
of expression was
really eye opening.

00:50:16.560 --> 00:50:19.090
As far as softening the ground
or not softening the ground,

00:50:19.090 --> 00:50:21.810
I think people view these
things in different ways.

00:50:21.810 --> 00:50:25.450
Sometimes people view
things as transactions,

00:50:25.450 --> 00:50:26.950
I think that's a
very limited way

00:50:26.950 --> 00:50:30.730
to view the world generally
speaking and ground comes

00:50:30.730 --> 00:50:32.830
in all different
kinds of states,

00:50:32.830 --> 00:50:34.990
but that we are all people
and the more we can learn

00:50:34.990 --> 00:50:37.290
from each other the
better we all are.

