00:52:23.700 --> 00:52:28.030
and it's really important
and matters to all of us

00:52:28.030 --> 00:52:31.430
and what are the efforts
that are being done to build

00:52:31.430 --> 00:52:35.040
that bridge, literature
bridge and break this idea

00:52:35.040 --> 00:52:38.660
that it's English versus
Spanish, if America is one

00:52:38.660 --> 00:52:40.300
and [inaudible] any
thoughts or ideas

00:52:40.300 --> 00:52:42.610
of how build this
bridge [inaudible]

00:52:42.610 --> 00:52:45.900
about the Americas
and not America?

