00:54:49.530 --> 00:54:53.450
to create readers for the
future because all the kids are

00:54:53.450 --> 00:55:00.430
with their cell phones and with
their pads and stuff like that,

00:55:00.430 --> 00:55:04.340
so in a way I feel that
before I could think

00:55:04.340 --> 00:55:08.070
of this broader idea I think
with stronger literacy and more,

00:55:08.070 --> 00:55:10.180
yeah, more access,
better access to books,

00:55:10.180 --> 00:55:11.480
I think it's a fight I would go

00:55:11.480 --> 00:55:13.550
for in my own country
to begin with.

