collaborate with each other

01:07:11.670 --> 01:07:15.780
and not view it as a
competition, I think is great.

01:07:15.780 --> 01:07:18.720
There are models out
there that I admire,

01:07:18.720 --> 01:07:21.810
I think that what the Brits
do, or what the British do

01:07:21.810 --> 01:07:24.820
with English in particular
is very impressive,

01:07:24.820 --> 01:07:27.560
